ActGovernment Property Traffic Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Government Property Traffic Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending the GOVERNMENT PROPERTY TRAFFIC REGULATIONS (Miscellaneous Program), in order to delete the words "all at the expense of the owner" from Section 19 of the Regulations, which the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations considers to be ultra vires of the Act.
